{"type":"message","id":"53f7b04c","parentId":"04f65aee","timestamp":"2026-03-16T15:49:41.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"安装完成，Sir！🎩\n\n**已安装：** `skill-finder-cn@1.0.0`\n\n**安装位置：** `C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\skill-finder-cn`\n\n让我查看一下这个技能的功能："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:34","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/Administrator/.openclaw/workspace/skills/skill-finder-cn/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":645,"output":91,"cacheRead":25600,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26336,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773676179414}}
{"type":"message","id":"1d9a136d","parentId":"53f7b04c","timestamp":"2026-03-16T15:49:41.687Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:34","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: skill-finder-cn\ndescription: \"Skill 查找器 | Skill Finder. 帮助发现和安装 ClawHub Skills | Discover and install ClawHub Skills. 回答'有什么技能可以X'、'找一个技能' | Answers 'what skill can X', 'find a skill'. 触发词：找 skill、find skill、搜索 skill.\"\nauthor: 赚钱小能手\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    emoji: 🔍\n    requires:\n      bins: [clawhub]\n---\n\n# Skill 查找器\n\n帮助用户发现和安装 ClawHub 上的 Skills。\n\n## 功能\n\n当用户问：\n- \"有什么 skill 可以帮我...？\"\n- \"找一个能做 X 的 skill\"\n- \"有没有 skill 可以...\"\n- \"我需要一个能...的 skill\"\n\n这个 Skill 会帮助搜索 ClawHub 并推荐相关的 Skills。\n\n## 使用方法\n\n### 1. 搜索 Skills\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"<用户需求>\"\n```\n\n### 2. 查看详情\n\n```bash\nclawhub inspect <skill-name>\n```\n\n### 3. 安装 Skill\n\n```bash\nclawhub install <skill-name>\n```\n\n## 工作流程\n\n```\n1. 理解用户需求\n2. 提取关键词\n3. 搜索 ClawHub\n4. 列出相关 Skills\n5. 提供安装建议\n```\n\n## 示例\n\n**用户**: \"有什么 skill 可以帮我监控加密货币价格？\"\n\n**搜索**: `clawhub search \"crypto price monitor\"`\n\n**返回**: 相关的 Skills 列表\n\n---\n\n*帮助用户发现需要的 Skills 🔍*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773676181685}}
{"type":"message","id":"aab3d8a0","parentId":"1d9a136d","timestamp":"2026-03-16T15:49:44.411Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**skill-finder-cn** 已就绪！🔍\n\n这是一个 Skill 查找器，可以帮助您发现和安装其他 ClawHub Skills。\n\n**触发方式：**\n- \"有什么 skill 可以帮我...？\"\n- \"找一个能做 X 的 skill\"\n- \"搜索 skill...\"\n- \"有没有 skill 可以...\"\n\n现在您可以直接问我类似的问题，我会自动使用这个技能来帮您搜索和推荐合适的技能。\n\n需要我现在演示一下，或者安装其他技能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":575,"output":100,"cacheRead":26112,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26787,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773676181688}}
