{"type":"message","id":"64b9e664","parentId":"547f47ee","timestamp":"2026-03-16T15:51:33.952Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"安装完成，Sir！🎩\n\n**已安装：** `openclaw-tavily-search@0.1.0`\n\n让我查看一下配置说明："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:38","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/Administrator/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-tavily-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":515,"output":72,"cacheRead":27648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28235,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773676291719}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f302257","parentId":"64b9e664","timestamp":"2026-03-16T15:51:33.971Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:38","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: tavily-search\ndescription: \"Web search via Tavily API (alternative to Brave). Use when the user asks to search the web / look up sources / find links and Brave web_search is unavailable or undesired. Returns a small set of relevant results (title, url, snippet) and can optionally include short answer summaries.\"\n---\n\n# Tavily Search\n\nUse the bundled script to search the web with Tavily.\n\n## Requirements\n\n- Provide API key via either:\n  - environment variable: `TAVILY_API_KEY`, or\n  - `~/.openclaw/.env` line: `TAVILY_API_KEY=...`\n\n## Commands\n\nRun from the OpenClaw workspace:\n\n```bash\n# raw JSON (default)\npython3 {baseDir}/scripts/tavily_search.py --query \"...\" --max-results 5\n\n# include short answer (if available)\npython3 {baseDir}/scripts/tavily_search.py --query \"...\" --max-results 5 --include-answer\n\n# stable schema (closer to web_search): {query, results:[{title,url,snippet}], answer?}\npython3 {baseDir}/scripts/tavily_search.py --query \"...\" --max-results 5 --format brave\n\n# human-readable Markdown list\npython3 {baseDir}/scripts/tavily_search.py --query \"...\" --max-results 5 --format md\n```\n\n## Output\n\n### raw (default)\n- JSON: `query`, optional `answer`, `results: [{title,url,content}]`\n\n### brave\n- JSON: `query`, optional `answer`, `results: [{title,url,snippet}]`\n\n### md\n- A compact Markdown list with title/url/snippet.\n\n## Notes\n\n- Keep `max-results` small by default (3–5) to reduce token/reading load.\n- Prefer returning URLs + snippets; fetch full pages only when needed.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773676293968}}
{"type":"message","id":"c801d61b","parentId":"6f302257","timestamp":"2026-03-16T15:51:36.911Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**openclaw-tavily-search** 已就绪！🔍\n\n这是一个 Tavily API 的网络搜索技能，可以作为 Brave 搜索的替代方案。\n\n**配置要求：**\n需要设置 `TAVILY_API_KEY`，通过以下任一方式：\n- 环境变量：`TAVILY_API_KEY`\n- 或写入文件：`~/.openclaw/.env` 添加 `TAVILY_API_KEY=your_key_here`\n\n**使用方法：**\n- 搜索网络内容\n- 查找资料来源\n- 获取链接和摘要\n\n您有 Tavily API Key 吗？需要我帮您配置吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":487,"output":131,"cacheRead":28160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28778,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773676293971}}
