{"type":"message","id":"53ff0c62","parentId":"ed082fb9","timestamp":"2026-03-16T16:14:16.255Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白，Sir。🎩\n\n**free-ride** 技能已安装并待命。当您需要使用时，只需告诉我，我会帮您：\n\n1. 获取 OpenRouter API Key\n2. 配置最佳免费模型\n3. 设置自动 fallback\n4. 重启 gateway 生效\n\n目前已安装的技能总结：\n\n| 技能 | 功能 |\n|-----|------|\n| 🔍 skill-finder-cn | Skill 查找器 |\n| 🔍 openclaw-tavily-search | Tavily 搜索（已配置 API） |\n| 🔍 multi-search-engine | 17引擎多搜索引擎 |\n| 📄 office-automation-test | 办公自动化（日报/周报/会议纪要） |\n| ⏰ cron-mastery | 定时任务管理 |\n| 📰 news-summary | 新闻摘要 |\n| 🚀 free-ride | 免费 AI 模型管理 |\n\n还有其他需要安装或配置的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":454,"output":192,"cacheRead":49920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50566,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773677651850}}
