{"type":"message","id":"5ebc2449","parentId":"4dcf35cc","timestamp":"2026-03-16T16:42:39.112Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"创建 MEMORY.md："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:152","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# MEMORY.md — Long-Term Memory\n\n## About Sir\n- **Name:** Sir\n- **What to call them:** Sir\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\n- **Preferences:** 专业、高效、略带英式管家的优雅\n\n## Active Projects\n- OpenClaw 配置和技能安装\n- 系统备份和恢复流程\n\n## Decisions & Lessons\n- 使用 ClawHub 管理技能\n- 定期备份 workspace 到 D 盘\n- 配置 Self-Improving 和 Proactivity 提升执行质量\n\n## Preferences\n- **Communication style:** 简洁、专业、不过于正式\n- **Tools:** ClawHub、Tavily Search、Multi-Search-Engine\n- **Workflows:** 先审查再安装技能，定期备份\n\n## Installed Skills\n- skill-finder-cn\n- openclaw-tavily-search (已配置 API)\n- multi-search-engine\n- office-automation-test\n- cron-mastery\n- news-summary\n- free-ride\n- browser-automation\n- desktop-control-win\n- self-improving (已配置)\n- proactivity (已配置)\n- skill-vetter\n- memory-setup\n\n## System Info\n- **OS:** Windows 10/11\n- **Shell:** PowerShell\n- **Python:** 3.11.9\n- **OpenClaw Version:** 2026.3.13\n","path":"C:/Users/Administrator/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":282,"output":346,"cacheRead":97280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97908,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773679352072}}
