{"type":"message","id":"1a588d39","parentId":"6c1daa9e","timestamp":"2026-03-16T16:42:44.319Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"配置完成，Sir！🐘\n\n**Memory Setup 已配置完成：**\n\n✅ **openclaw.json 已更新：**\n- 添加 `memorySearch` 配置\n- 使用 `local` 提供商（无需 API Key）\n- 索引来源：`memory` 和 `sessions`\n- 实时索引模式\n\n✅ **记忆文件结构已创建：**\n```\nworkspace/\n├── MEMORY.md              ✅ 已创建\n└── memory/\n    ├── logs/              ✅ 每日日志\n    ├── projects/          ✅ 项目特定上下文\n    ├── groups/            ✅ 群组聊天上下文\n    └── system/            ✅ 偏好、设置笔记\n```\n\n✅ **MEMORY.md 已初始化：**\n- 关于 Sir 的信息\n- 活跃项目\n- 决策和教训\n- 偏好设置\n- 已安装技能列表\n- 系统信息\n\n**需要重启 Gateway 使配置生效吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":407,"output":201,"cacheRead":97536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98144,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773679359132}}
